// CM reinforced


Given	I'm logged-in with valid credentials
And	I'm on Page 03 of Shoulder MRI
When	I select the radio button 'Yes' in Contrast enhanced
Then	'Active ingredient' dropdown menu is enabled
And	'Volume of contrast agent (GBCA)' input field is enabled
And 'Intravenous' checkbox is enabled
And 'Intraarticular' checkbox is enabled
And	'Adverse reaction' checkbox is enabled

When I select 'Intravenous' checkbox
Then 'Indirect MR arthrography' checkbox is enabled

When I select 'Intraarticular' checkbox
Then 'Dilution (5 - 500 possible)' input field is enabled
